#: data/campaigns/Two_Brothers/scenarios/3_Guarded_Castle.cfg:417
#: data/campaigns/Two_Brothers/scenarios/3_Guarded_Castle.cfg:425
#: data/campaigns/Two_Brothers/scenarios/3_Guarded_Castle.cfg:434
